<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔

				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>Gain great rewards for
any full board!</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>Jackpot multipliers for
great rewards!</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>Le scommesse extra devono pagare 
un 50% aggiuntivo dell'importo della scommessa.
Con le scommesse extra attivate.
Il Moltiplicatore Vincente Deve Essere X2 o Maggiore.
La Ruota della Fortuna ottiene un moltiplicatore casuale.</EXTRA_TIPS>
	</dict>
</plist>

		<WIN_TITLE>赢分</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>b;18;WILD,w;18;可代替除,b;18;长城、龙,w;18;以外,w;18;</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>w;18;的所有符号，WILD会出现在</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>b;18;2、3、4、5,w;18;的转轮中。 </TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;特殊赔率</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;22;数量</TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;22;赔率</TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;免费游戏</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>w;18;当第,b;18;1、2、3、4、5、6</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>w;18;轮，出现长城时，即可进入</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>w;18;免费游戏。 </TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>w;18;1.起始局数为,b;18;8,w;18;局，单局得分倍数为1。 </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>w;18;2.当出现,b;18;龙,w;18;图案时，每个龙可累积「,b;18;累积局数,,w;18;」,b;18;1,w;18;局，但不会获得奖励。 </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>

		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4.免费游戏于「累积局数」与「免费游戏局数」皆为 0 时结束。 </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>w;18;5.免费游戏的连线奖金计算方式为 ,b;18;押注额 X 连线数 X 赔率 X 得分倍数, w;18;。 </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>

		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>w;18;1.从,b;18;最左轮,w;18;算起，有连续3个以上相同图案，</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>Gain great rewards for
any full board!</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>Jackpot multipliers for
great rewards!</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>Pariurile suplimentare trebuie să
plătească un supliment de 50% din suma pariului.
Cu pariurile suplimentare activate.
Multiplicatorul câștigător trebuie să fie X2 sau mai mare.
Roata Norocului primește un multiplicator aleatoriu.</EXTRA_TIPS>
	</dict>
</plist>

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>Gain great rewards for
any full board!</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>Jackpot multipliers for
great rewards!</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>Οι επιπρόσθετες στοιχηματικές πρέπει να
πληρώσουν επιπλέον 50% του ποσού του στοιχήματος.
Με τα επιπρόσθετα στοιχήματα ενεργοποιημένα.
Ο Πολλαπλασιαστής Νικητή Πρέπει Να Είναι Χ2 Ή Περισσότερο.
Το Τυχερό Τροχός Παίρνει Τυχαίο Πολλαπλασιαστή.</EXTRA_TIPS>
	</dict>
</plist>

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>Ganhe grandes recompensas em qualquer pensão completa!</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>Multiplicadores de jackpot para grandes recompensas!</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>Extra bets need to pay an additional 50% of the betting amount.
Extra bets will only appear the rates other than the general bet 1x.
Lucky Wheel gets random multiplier.</EXTRA_TIPS>
		
	</dict>
</plist>

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中

					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>

		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>Gain great rewards for
any full board!</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>Jackpot multipliers for
great rewards!</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>An additional 50% of the bet 
is required to pay for the Extra Bets.
In Extra Bet mode, 1x multiplier symbol will be
removed from the special reel. 
In Extra Bet mode,
the prize value on the Lucky Wheel will be multiplied
by a random multiplier which could be: 1x, 2x, 3x, 5x, 10x, 15x.</EXTRA_TIPS>
	</dict>
</plist>

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>Thưởng khủng toàn bàn bất kỳ</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>Nhân thêm bội số nổ thưởng khủng</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>Mức cược thêm sẽ là 50% của mức cược ban đầu.
Khi kích hoạt mức cược thêm, bội số bảo đảm x2 trở lên.
Bánh xe may mắn nhận được số nhân ngẫu nhiên.</EXTRA_TIPS>
		
	</dict>
</plist>

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">

	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定義方式 start
			如果設定一段文字同時具有不同顏色，則需要特別設定。
			設定方式如下：
				顏色;字型大小;實際顯示文字 <=此為每段文字所需包含的內容，每個屬性使用" ; "分隔
				顏色;字型大小;段落1,顏色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落設定之間使用" , "分隔
				
				顏色定義：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增請加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的設定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				範例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符號，WILD會出現在每條轉輪中。
					可參考各遊戲說明的製作方式
					
				備註：
					純色的text替換不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但單一UI請保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定義方式 end -->

		<!-- Auto Play start -->
		<!-- <AUTO_PLAY_FREE_STOP>進入「免費遊戲」停止</AUTO_PLAY_FREE_STOP> -->
		<!-- <AUTO_PLAY_BONUS_STOP>進入「赤壁之戰」停止</AUTO_PLAY_BONUS_STOP> -->
		<!-- Auto Play end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>贏分</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 賠付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>b;18;WILD,w;18;可代替除,b;18;長城、龍,w;18;以外,w;18;</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>w;18;的所有符號，WILD會出現在</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>b;18;2、3、4、5,w;18;的轉輪中。</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;特殊賠率</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;22;數量</TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;22;賠率</TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;免費遊戲</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>w;18;當第,b;18;1、2、3、4、5、6</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>w;18;輪，出現長城時，即可進入</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>w;18;免費遊戲。</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>w;18;1.起始局數為,b;18;8,w;18;局，單局得分倍數為1。</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>w;18;2.當出現 ,b;18;龍 ,w;18;圖案時，每個龍可累積「,b;18;累積局數,,w;18;」,b;18;1,w;18;局，但不會獲得獎勵。</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>w;18;3.下一回的免費遊戲，單局「得分倍數」將會加,b;18;1,w;18;。</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4.免費遊戲於「累積局數」與「免費遊戲局數」皆為 0 時結束。</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>w;18;5.免費遊戲的連線獎金計算方式為  ,b;18;押注額 X 連線數 X 賠率 X 得分倍數, w;18;。</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;遊戲規則</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>w;18;1.從,b;18;最左輪,w;18;算起，有連續3個以上相同圖案，</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>w;18;即可獲得連線獎金。</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>w;18;2.遊戲中所有中獎圖案會再燃燒出,b;18;新的圖案,w;18;，</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>w;18;並重新對獎。當無法對獎時，即可取得該局</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>w;18;分數。</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>w;18;3.總共有,b;18;4096,w;18;種得獎方式。</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>任意全盤高額獎勵</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>加乘倍率爆大獎</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
	<dict>
		<!-- RICH TEXT 定义方式 start
			如果设定一段文字同时具有不同颜色，则需要特别设定。
			设定方式如下：
				颜色;字型大小;实际显示文字 <=此为每段文字所需包含的内容，每个属性使用" ; "分隔
				颜色;字型大小;段落1,颜色;字型大小;段落2 <=段落设定之间使用" , "分隔
				
				颜色定义：
					COLOR_WHITE = "w",
					COLOR_GREEN = "g",
					COLOR_BLUE = "b",
					COLOR_RED = "r",
					COLOR_ORANGE = "o",
					如有新增请加入Define.lua - RichTextSetting，且把c3b的设定加入GlobalFunc.lua - GetColor中
				
				范例：
					b;22;WILD,w;22;可替代除,b;22;SCATTER,w;22;以外的所有符号，WILD会出现在每条转轮中。
					可参考各游戏说明的制作方式
					
				备注：
					纯色的text替换不需要使用到rich text，直接使用studio的label(text)即可，但单一UI请保持一致性。
			RICH TEXT 定义方式 end -->

		<WIN_TITLE>WIN</WIN_TITLE>

		<!-- 赔付表 -->
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>WILD can substitutes for any\nsymbol except BONUS\nSYMBOL and SCATTER\nSYMBOL.\n\nWIDL appears in 2,3,4 and\n5 reels.</TWK_PG1_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG1_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>y;30;SCATTER</TWK_PG2_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_1>b;18;AMOUNT  </TWK_PG2_TXT_1>
		<TWK_PG2_TXT_2>b;18;Payoff Odds  </TWK_PG2_TXT_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>y;30;FREE GAME</TWK_PG3_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>Collect SCATTER SYMBOL\non reel 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 \nto trigger FREE GAME.</TWK_PG3_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG3_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>1. Free game starts with 8 rounds, the mutiple begins with 1.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_1>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>2. Collect SCATTER SYMBOL in free game to get one more round.\nAnd don't get SCATTER AWARD.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_2>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>3. Each win in free spin are multiplied by the current free spin round.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_3>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>4. Free game ends when there are no more rounds.</TWK_PG3_TXT_2_4>
		<TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>5. Free game's award is  bet x line x paid x multiple. </TWK_PG3_TXT_2_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>y;30;Rule</TWK_PG4_TITLE_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>1. There are more than three same symbols,\nthen players can get award according to the\npaytable.</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_1>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_2>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_3>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>2. There are 4096 way!</TWK_PG4_TXT_1_4>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_5>
		<TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6></TWK_PG4_TXT_1_6>
		<!-- 赔付表 end -->

		<!-- 特色頁 -->
		<TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>임의의 전체 판 대량의 보상</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>
		<TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>배가 배율 보상 팡팡</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>
		<!-- 特色頁 end -->

		<EXTRA_TIPS>추가 베팅 시 별도로 50%의 베팅 금액를 지불해야 합니다.
추가 베팅 시작, 득점 배율 배가 2X 이상 확정
행운의 바퀴는 임의의 승수를 얻습니다.</EXTRA_TIPS>
		
	</dict>
</plist>

any full board!</TWK_FEATURES_LEFT>

great rewards!</TWK_FEATURES_RIGHT>

		<EXTRA_TIPS>Extra bets need to pay an additional 50% of the betting amount.
Extra bets will only appear the rates other than the general bet 1x.
